      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/al-kafi:7:3:33:2",
      "text": [
        " مَنْ شَرِبَ الْخَمْرَ فَاجْلِدُوهُ فَإِنْ عَادَ فَاجْلِدُوهُ فَإِنْ عَادَ فَاقْتُلُوهُ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Abu Ali Al Ashary, from Muhammad Bin Abdul Jabbar, from Safwan, from Mansour Bin Hazim, from Abu Ubeyda, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘The one who drinks the wine, so whip him. So if he repeats, so whip him. So if he repeats, so kill him’."
        ]
